{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/addyosmani/critical-path-css-tools/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"182cdca9-af50-5d06-b819-aa84089e5770","html":"<h1 id=\"critical-path-above-the-fold-css-tools-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#critical-path-above-the-fold-css-tools-awesome\" aria-label=\"critical path above the fold css tools awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Critical-path (Above-the-fold) CSS Tools <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tools to help prioritize above-the-fold CSS</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"prioritize-above-the-fold-content-first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prioritize-above-the-fold-content-first\" aria-label=\"prioritize above the fold content first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prioritize above-the-fold content first.</h3>\n<p>For best performance, PageSpeed Insights <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/PrioritizeVisibleContent\">recommends</a> inlining the critical (above-the-fold) CSS of your page directly into your HTML. This eliminates additional roundtrips and allows the browser to paint the above-fold experience to your user's screen sooner. The main idea is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Determine the above-the-fold styles for a page and write them between <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style&gt;</code> tags in the head.</li>\n<li>Load all other stylesheets in the footer, ideally asynchronously.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The following is a list of tools to help generate, inline and report on critical-path CSS.</p>\n<h2 id=\"node-modules\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#node-modules\" aria-label=\"node modules permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Node modules</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pocketjoso/penthouse\">Penthouse</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/pocketjoso/penthouse\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.5k</span></span></a> - by Jonas Ohlsson generates critical-path CSS</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/critical\">Critical</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/critical\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">9.6k</span></span></a> - by Addy Osmani generates &#x26; inlines critical-path CSS (uses Penthouse, <a href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/oust\">Oust</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/oust\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">163</span></span></a> and inline-styles)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/criticalcss\">CriticalCSS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/criticalcss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.7k</span></span></a> - by FilamentGroup finds &#x26; outputs critical CSS</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"server-side-modules\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#server-side-modules\" aria-label=\"server side modules permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Server-side modules</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pagespeed/mod_pagespeed\">mod_pagespeed</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/pagespeed/mod_pagespeed\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">689</span></span></a> - Apache module for automatic PageSpeed optimization</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pagespeed/ngx_pagespeed\">ngx_pagespeed</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/pagespeed/ngx_pagespeed\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.4k</span></span></a> - Nginx module for automatic PageSpeed optimization</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"grunt-tasks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grunt-tasks\" aria-label=\"grunt tasks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grunt tasks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fatso83/grunt-penthouse\">grunt-penthouse</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fatso83/grunt-penthouse\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">68</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/grunt-criticalcss\">grunt-critical-css</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/grunt-criticalcss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">533</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bezoerb/grunt-critical\">grunt-critical</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bezoerb/grunt-critical\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">148</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"casperjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#casperjs\" aria-label=\"casperjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CasperJS</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ibrennan/critical-css-casperjs\">critical-css-casperjs</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ibrennan/critical-css-casperjs\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">68</span></span></a> - CasperJS script to pull critical CSS information from pages</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"phantomjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#phantomjs\" aria-label=\"phantomjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PhantomJS</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/drdk/dr-css-inliner\">dr-css-inliner</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/drdk/dr-css-inliner\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">81</span></span></a> - PhantomJS script to inline above-the-fold CSS on a page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"inline-sources-styles-scripts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inline-sources-styles-scripts\" aria-label=\"inline sources styles scripts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inline sources (styles, scripts)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/maxogden/inline-styles\">inline-styles</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/maxogden/inline-styles\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24</span></span></a> - by Max Ogden, replaces <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link&gt;</code> tags with inline <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style&gt;</code> tags + inlines CSS url() calls with data URIs</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fmal/gulp-inline-source\">gulp-inline-source</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fmal/gulp-inline-source\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">211</span></span></a> - by Filip Malinowski, replaces <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link&gt;</code> tags with inline <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style&gt;</code> tags, and replaces <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script src=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code> tags with their inline content</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bezoerb/inline-critical\">inline-critical</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bezoerb/inline-critical\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">106</span></span></a> - by Ben Zörb, inline critical path CSS and load existing stylesheets with <code class=\"language-text\">loadCSS</code></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/kriasoft/isomorphic-style-loader/\">isomorphic-style-loader</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/kriasoft/isomorphic-style-loader/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a> for Webpack - allows to extract critical CSS for any given page/screen in React apps and inline it into HTML during server-side rendering (SSR). See <a href=\"https://github.com/kriasoft/react-starter-kit\">React Starter Kit</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/kriasoft/react-starter-kit\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">21.5k</span></span></a> as an example.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"async-load-css\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#async-load-css\" aria-label=\"async load css permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Async load CSS</h2>\n<p>Async loading should be used to fetch the rest of your site-wide styles after you've inlined your critical-path CSS.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/loadCSS\">loadCSS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/filamentgroup/loadCSS\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.8k</span></span></a> - loads CSS asynchronously using JS. <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/scottjehl/87176715419617ae6994\">Research</a> that led to this is also available.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/matt-bailey/602b40c77a5d3381ff26\">async &#x26; conditional loading</a> - POC script for loading CSS files asynchronously and conditionally based on body tag classes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/n0mad01/asyncLoader\">asyncLoader</a> - async script/stylesheet loader</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://addyosmani.github.io/basket.js/\">basket.js</a> - async script/resource loader with support for localStorage caching. Can be <a href=\"https://github.com/andrewwakeling/basket-css-example\">extended</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/andrewwakeling/basket-css-example\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">19</span></span></a> to load stylesheets.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note: The Guardian currently also cache their global styles into localStorage for subsequent page loads. More info in this <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/scottjehl/87176715419617ae6994\">comment</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"online-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#online-tools\" aria-label=\"online tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Online tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://jonassebastianohlsson.com/criticalpathcssgenerator/\">Penthouse online</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"bookmarkletsextensions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bookmarkletsextensions\" aria-label=\"bookmarkletsextensions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bookmarklets/Extensions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/PaulKinlan/6284142\">Snippet</a> by Paul Kinlan. Patrick Hamann has an <a href=\"http://patrickhamann.com/workshops/performance/tasks/2_Critical_Path/2_2.html\">exercise</a> using the snippet you can try out.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/scottjehl/b6129da04733e4e0f9a4\">Snippet</a> by Scott Jehl</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ndreckshage/CSSVacuum\">CSSVacuum</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ndreckshage/CSSVacuum\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">45</span></span></a> by ndreckshage</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"render-blocking-issues-detection\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#render-blocking-issues-detection\" aria-label=\"render blocking issues detection permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Render-blocking issues detection</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/\">PageSpeed Insights</a> - Online tool that measures the performance of a page for mobile devices and desktop devices. It fetches the url twice, once with a mobile user-agent, and once with a desktop-user agent.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/psi\">PSI</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/psi\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.1k</span></span></a> - Node module for PageSpeed Insights reporting as part of your build process. Use directly with Gulp or use <a href=\"https://github.com/jrcryer/grunt-pagespeed\">grunt-pagespeed</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jrcryer/grunt-pagespeed\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">464</span></span></a> if a Grunt user. For local testing, a write-up using this task and <a href=\"http://www.jamescryer.com/2014/06/12/grunt-pagespeed-and-ngrok-locally-testing/\">ngrok</a> is available.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pagespeed-insights-by-goo/gplegfbjlmmehdoakndmohflojccocli?hl=en\">PageSpeed Insights DevTools extension</a> - Chrome extension for running PageSpeed tests from inside the browser.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pagespeed-insights-checke/mkjmodmicmpjedhoekkmafdgpocdkbna?hl=en\">PageSpeed Insights Checker for mobile extension</a> - checks Mobile PageSpeed score for every page and gives you a handy preview.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"supplementary-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#supplementary-tools\" aria-label=\"supplementary tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Supplementary tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/giakki/uncss\">UnCSS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/giakki/uncss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">9.3k</span></span></a> removes unused CSS from pages, allowing you to reduce the global CSS you may need to load in for your site. Tasks are available for <a href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/grunt-uncss\">Grunt</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/addyosmani/grunt-uncss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.9k</span></span></a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/ben-eb/gulp-uncss\">Gulp</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ben-eb/gulp-uncss\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">961</span></span></a> and <a href=\"https://addyosmani.com/blog/removing-unused-css/\">other</a> build tools.</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#critical-path-above-the-fold-css-tools-awesome\">Critical-path (Above-the-fold) CSS Tools <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#prioritize-above-the-fold-content-first\">Prioritize above-the-fold content first.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#node-modules\">Node modules</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#server-side-modules\">Server-side modules</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#grunt-tasks\">Grunt tasks</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#casperjs\">CasperJS</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#phantomjs\">PhantomJS</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#inline-sources-styles-scripts\">Inline sources (styles, scripts)</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#async-load-css\">Async load CSS</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#online-tools\">Online tools</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#bookmarkletsextensions\">Bookmarklets/Extensions</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#render-blocking-issues-detection\">Render-blocking issues detection</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#supplementary-tools\">Supplementary tools</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"critical-path-above-the-fold-css-tools-awesome","value":"Critical-path (Above-the-fold) CSS Tools Awesome","depth":1},{"id":"prioritize-above-the-fold-content-first","value":"Prioritize above-the-fold content first.","depth":3},{"id":"node-modules","value":"Node modules","depth":2},{"id":"server-side-modules","value":"Server-side modules","depth":2},{"id":"grunt-tasks","value":"Grunt tasks","depth":2},{"id":"casperjs","value":"CasperJS","depth":2},{"id":"phantomjs","value":"PhantomJS","depth":2},{"id":"inline-sources-styles-scripts","value":"Inline sources (styles, scripts)","depth":2},{"id":"async-load-css","value":"Async load CSS","depth":2},{"id":"online-tools","value":"Online tools","depth":2},{"id":"bookmarkletsextensions","value":"Bookmarklets/Extensions","depth":2},{"id":"render-blocking-issues-detection","value":"Render-blocking issues detection","depth":2},{"id":"supplementary-tools","value":"Supplementary tools","depth":2}]},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2022-10-14T06:58:26.928Z","repo":"addyosmani/critical-path-css-tools","description":"Tools to prioritize above-the-fold (critical-path) CSS","readmeItemsUpdatedTime":1453318809000,"descriptionHTML":"<div>Tools to prioritize above-the-fold (critical-path) CSS</div>","stargazerCount":1129,"category":"Front-End Development"},"previous":{"id":"8d1b42af-9583-54f3-a731-91c24e519763","fields":{"repo":"awesome-css-group/awesome-css","slug":"/awesome-css-group/awesome-css/readme"}},"next":{"id":"51764d7e-bbd1-5137-8b36-66facbbc84f9","fields":{"repo":"davidtheclark/scalable-css-reading-list","slug":"/davidtheclark/scalable-css-reading-list/readme"}}},"pageContext":{"repo":"addyosmani/critical-path-css-tools","id":"182cdca9-af50-5d06-b819-aa84089e5770","previousId":"8d1b42af-9583-54f3-a731-91c24e519763","nextId":"51764d7e-bbd1-5137-8b36-66facbbc84f9"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}